sentence: please provide round trip flight information from nashville to memphis cost under one thousand dollars flights before noon

SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_days||'"', v0.departure_time,
 v0.arrival_time, '"'||v0.airline_flight||'"', '"'||v0.airline_code||'"',
 v0.flight_number, '"'||v0.aircraft_code_sequence||'"',
 '"'||v0.meal_code||'"', v0.stops, v0.connections, '"'||v0.dual_carrier||'"',
 v0.time_elapsed, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.flight_id||'"', '"'||v6.fare_id||'"', v6.round_trip_cost FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2,
 airport_service v3, city v4, flight_fare v5, fare v6 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'NASHVILLE'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'MEMPHIS'))) AND ((v0.departure_time <  1200) 
AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) 
AND ((v5.fare_id = ANY v6.fare_id) AND (v6.round_trip_cost <  1000))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID , FLIGHT.FLIGHT_DAYS , FLIGHT.FROM_AIRPORT , FLIGHT.TO_AIRPORT , FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME , FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME , FLIGHT.AIRLINE_FLIGHT , FLIGHT.AIRLINE_CODE , FLIGHT.FLIGHT_NUMBER , FLIGHT.AIRCRAFT_CODE_SEQUENCE , FLIGHT.MEAL_CODE , FLIGHT.STOPS , FLIGHT.CONNECTIONS , FLIGHT.DUAL_CARRIER , FLIGHT.TIME_ELAPSED FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' NASHVILLE ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MEMPHIS ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME < 1200 AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FARE . FARE_ID FROM FARE WHERE FARE.ROUND_TRIP_COST < 1000 ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
